# Firebase / FCM / APNs / Apple keys — keep out of the repo (true secrets;
# EAS / the host secret manager supply them at build/submit time).
# google-services.json          → Android Firebase config (place at apps/mobile/)
# google-service-account*.json  → FCM V1 push key + Play Console submit key
# *.p8 / .apns-key.p8           → APNs auth key (Apple push private key)
# .fcm-service-account.json     → FCM V1 service-account private key
# GoogleService-Info.plist      → iOS Firebase config (this app does NOT use it — see IOS_LAUNCH §1)
# .firebase-sha-fingerprints.txt / .apns-metadata.txt → captured credential metadata
google-services.json
google-service-account*.json
*.p8
.fcm-service-account.json
GoogleService-Info.plist
.firebase-sha-fingerprints.txt
.apns-metadata.txt

